name: intake-pattern-catalog
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "2022.1.0" %}
package:
  name: intake-pattern-catalog
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/i/intake-pattern-catalog/intake-pattern-catalog-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 960630e6f533d9f94b1470e28a232cf7fa83d9a4d7528779239beb1dbe135097

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vvv

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.6
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.6
    - fsspec >=2021.4.0
    - intake
    - s3fs
    - msgpack-python

test:
  imports:
    - intake_pattern_catalog
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://bitbucket.org/dtnse/intake_pattern_catalog
  summary: Intake plugin for specifying a file-path pattern which can represent a number of different entries⏎
  license_file: LICENSE.md
  license: BSD-3-Clause

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - raybellwaves
    - tdhopper
    - blackary
